OL,3,CScotland get set for Brazil as England
OL,4,Cdraw against Ghana
OL,6,FWorld Cup fever has been gripping both
OL,7,Fsides of the Border region as Scotland
OL,8,Fand England continue their 2026 North
OL,9,FAmerican journeys.
OL,11,FFor Scotland, history is on the line
OL,12,Fahead of their final group stage match
OL,13,Fagainst Brazil in Miami knowing a draw
OL,14,For a win will see them progress out of
OL,15,Fa World Cup group for the very first
OL,16,Ftime.
OL,18,FSteve Clarke's side currently sit
OL,19,Fthird in Group C after a 1-0 win and
OL,20,Fdefeat against Haiti and Morocco.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
