OL,3,CScotland get set for Brazil as England
OL,4,Cdraw against Ghana
OL,6,FThe side includes Dumfries' Grant
OL,7,FHanley and Lyndon Dykes, with the duo
OL,8,Flooking to feature against the South
OL,9,FAmerican giants on Wednesday.
OL,11,FWhile thousands of Tartan Army
OL,12,Ffaithful have travelled to Miami for
OL,13,Fthe game, excitement has been building
OL,14,Fin Scotland with fans expected to pack
OL,15,Fout the pubs and bars showing the game.
OL,17,FEngland meanwhile are currently
OL,18,Fsitting top of Group L with four
OL,19,Fpoints from their opening two games.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
