OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F321A1782296300
OL,3,CScotland get set for Brazil as England
OL,4,Cdraw against Ghana
OL,6,FThomas Tuchel's side turned heads for
OL,7,Ftheir impressive win against Croatia
OL,8,Fbefore a sobering draw against Ghana.
OL,10,FFans were packed out at Carlisle
OL,11,FUnited's Brunton Park on Tuesday
OL,12,Fevening hoping to see victory - but
OL,13,Fthey left feeling frustrated.
OL,15,FEngland are through after their two
OL,16,Fmatches played, but they will be
OL,17,Fhoping to defeat Panama and finish top
OL,18,Fof their group.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
